column1: Baby Barnaby's////This is my fail safe goto place for Brunch. The Green Eggs are a must try. The green eggs come out juicy
column2: moist and perfectly cooked every time at this location
column3: the original. The other locations are newer and shiner but have overcooked eggs. The servers here are friendly and know everybody's name
column4: they've been there since I moved to Houston.
